arget=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/712386/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"bf53878245a8d49438eec8b9f9c67cc8af6392f2","tid":718241,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:01:52.000Z","msg":"清"},{"pid":"da954a069f89074e356e0b4412761f37e599abcd","tid":718241,"uid":160122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf53878245a8d49438eec8b9f9c67cc8af6392f2","tid":718241,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:01:52.000Z","msg":"清"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:02:42.000Z","msg":"貨"},{"pid":"6be628a154b366114ecff1b3b292fba7ce8666fc","tid":718241,"uid":160122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"ROG list算係有誠意小小，起碼specify咗ROG料走盞空間小啲<br />\n<br />\n不過其實STRIX板個range都唔算細（900 - 1800），你以為i7 K系配隻Z370過你玩overclocking，其實可能出隻B360都唔定&hellip;咁出粒K系U又似乎多餘（non-K 平五舊）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/27/000932_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F000932_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG&h=26a2c9b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又係其他料盡平<br />\n<br />\n機箱多個ROG嘜頭就貴咗幾舊水，扺唔扺就睇你係咪教徒<br />\n（持貨者表示塊板跟嚟啲sticker都夠黐勻機箱）"},{"pid":"a5a4cef761bdb73c52b5de1f2aef794e4b451ad0","tid":718241,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6be628a154b366114ecff1b3b292fba7ce8666fc","tid":718241,"uid":160122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"ROG list算係有誠意小小，起碼specify咗ROG料走盞空間小啲<br />\n<br />\n不過其實STRIX板個range都唔算細（900 - 1800），你以為i7 K系配隻Z370過你玩overclocking，其實可能出隻B360都唔定&hellip;咁出粒K系U又似乎多餘（non-K 平五舊）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/27/000932_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F000932_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG&h=26a2c9b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又係其他料盡平<br />\n<br />\n機箱多個ROG嘜頭就貴咗幾舊水，扺唔扺就睇你係咪教徒<br />\n（持貨者表示塊板跟嚟啲sticker都夠黐勻機箱）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T23:49:26.000Z","msg":"做乜唔用dual ram"},{"pid":"fd666f618cc3496ffe94153c31eda2f9d845fa46","tid":718241,"uid":160122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:29:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ROG list算係有誠意小小，起碼specify咗ROG料走盞空間小啲<br />\n<br />\n不過其實STRIX板個range都唔算細（900 - 1800），你以為i7 K系配隻Z370過你玩overclocking，其實可能出隻B360都唔定&hellip;咁出粒K系U又似乎多餘（non-K 平五舊）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/27/000932_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F000932_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG&h=26a2c9b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又係其他料<span style=\"color: red;\">盡平</span><br />\n<br />\n機箱多個ROG嘜頭就貴咗幾舊水，扺唔扺就睇你係咪教徒<br />\n（持貨者表示塊板跟嚟啲sticker都夠黐勻機箱）</blockquote>做乜唔用dual ram</blockquote><br />\n因為OP個list無specify到dual 8G囉<br />\n<br />\n我個係還原list（worst case）嚟咋，即係商家有心昆水嘅話，交咁嘅貨meet哂字面條件你都吹佢唔漲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">並不代表本人建議</span><br />\n<br />\n<del>另：原來其實我又遺漏咗RAM係有RGB的</del>"},{"pid":"ff143b23335c0999400fe4f9828620bcdb5752da","tid":718241,"uid":160122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T02:28:08.000Z","msg":"完整還原完成&hellip;咁樣或者比較有得討論下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/27/100005_a19ddbe22afc139c538bfca41cea40ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F100005_a19ddbe22afc139c538bfca41cea40ad.png&h=6ac8fa52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲料算誠實，散買目前價睇嚟都係萬四水平<br />\n<br />\nCatch<br />\n1. 又要用K CPU，RAM用2666MHz?（唔識overclock）<br />\n2. 難怪機箱都要加埋ROG嘜頭，不過都係嗰句扺唔扺就睇你點睇<br />\n3. 我個人真係覺得條list係OK的，但係堂堂大代理，明明啲料用乜可以清清楚楚唔使施縮，係要搞到好有昆人水嘅味道咁<br />\n<del>4. 其實原價都未必去到二萬啩（launch price？）</del>"}]}